{"id":635462,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/【立此存照】是抗疫女护士？还是兼职演员？/","date":"2020-02-15T02:32:58Z","modified":"2020-02-15T02:35:44Z","title":"【立此存照】看官媒如何造新闻：是抗疫女护士？还是兼职演员？","content":"<p>2月7日，澎湃新闻视频报道<a href=\"https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_5820765\">《战疫者丨女护士隔玻璃凝望男友：抱抱我》</a>拍摄了浙大四院感染楼门口，95后护士陈颖与男友隔门对望的场景。视频中还借女护士之口提及了一些“动人细节”：例如“等疫情结束，第一件事就是领证。”</p>\n<p>原<a href=\"https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_5820765\">视频</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635463\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"422\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者.png 1184w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者-300x230.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者-1024x785.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者-768x589.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者-1080x828.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这则报道发布后，引起了部分网友对其真实性的质疑，例如：</p>\n<p>视频中明显出现一些越肩拍摄镜头，从清晰度上看也应该是专业单反级设备。当然这可以理解为是来自记者的拍摄。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者2-9.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635464\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者2-9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"308\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者2-9.png 1860w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者2-9-300x168.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者2-9-1024x573.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者2-9-768x429.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者2-9-1536x859.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者2-9-1080x604.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>但视频中却出现了多次明显的机位视角变换，这些机位变化显示出记者拍摄时位置时而在室内时而在室外，那该护士的男友为何不像记者那样进入，或者该女护士为何不像记者那样出来呢？</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者3-6.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635465\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者3-6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"306\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者3-6.png 1836w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者3-6-300x167.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者3-6-1024x570.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者3-6-768x428.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者3-6-1536x855.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者3-6-1080x601.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这样的机位切换出现了数次：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者4-5.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635466\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者4-5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"305\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者4-5.png 1858w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者4-5-300x167.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者4-5-1024x569.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者4-5-768x427.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者4-5-1536x853.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者4-5-1080x600.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者5-3.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635467\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者5-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"309\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者5-3.png 1858w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者5-3-300x169.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者5-3-1024x575.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者5-3-768x432.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者5-3-1536x863.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者5-3-1080x607.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>最后甚至有记者跟随女护士搭电梯返回的镜头：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者6-4.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635470\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者6-4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"308\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者6-4.png 1862w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者6-4-300x168.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者6-4-1024x574.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者6-4-768x431.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者6-4-1536x861.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者6-4-1080x606.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>而这段视频部分拍摄画面稳定无抖动，视频中也确实多次出现了三脚架穿帮镜头：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者7-3.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635472\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者7-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"310\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者7-3.png 1858w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者7-3-300x169.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者7-3-1024x576.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者7-3-768x432.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者7-3-1536x865.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者7-3-1080x608.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者8.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635473\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"309\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者8.png 1866w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者8-300x168.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者8-1024x575.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者8-768x431.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者8-1536x863.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者8-1080x607.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>有网友也发现了此点：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQu4sPgU0AID_WM.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635475\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQu4sPgU0AID_WM.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"487\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQu4sPgU0AID_WM.jpeg 1081w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQu4sPgU0AID_WM-300x292.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQu4sPgU0AID_WM-1024x997.jpeg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQu4sPgU0AID_WM-768x747.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQu4sPgU0AID_WM-50x50.jpeg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>但在有三脚架镜头穿帮的时候，也就是该段视频“最煽情处”，我们却可以发现视频出现了画面抖动（第20秒位置）：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者11-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635474\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者11-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"127\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者11-1.png 2002w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者11-1-300x69.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者11-1-1024x236.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者11-1-768x177.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者11-1-1536x354.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/战疫者11-1-1080x249.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>很显然记者只是在室内才使用了三脚架，而在室外为了图省事并没有，这也显示出他肯定有过进出，而非使用两个独立的固定机位来进行拍摄（室内+室外），记者又如何得知私密的情侣见面时间及地点？整个隔窗相望的场景，显得摆拍痕迹极其明显。</p>\n<p><strong>以下为中国数字时代摘自部分网友评论：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>@张****博：看着我义乌的浙四医院，深深的感触：摄像头的机位一会在里面拍一会在外面拍，反正摄影和记者想在哪里拍就在哪里拍，但是你们两个！就是一个不能出！！一个不能进！！这是剧本，必须服从！！</p>\n<p>@B*****sa ： 里面摆拍摄像机瞩目。</p>\n<p>@Pa***ster：记者怎么捕捉到的？提前通知记者？还能内外取景？</p>\n<p>@凡****：因为政府要宣传，给了这一对牛郎织女这个机会。</p>\n<p>@模*****阿里：任何一对恋爱中的情侣，见不着面开视频就好。男朋友没必要这个时候去秀恩爱，去给抗击肺炎添乱。</p>\n<p>@Ro*****僧了：我要是跟我对象说悄悄话，肯定避开别人，这么私密的事，让别人传到网上就更别扭了。</p>\n<p>@俗*****个：有个疑问………记者怎么进去的拍摄的！就小伙子进不去只能在外面。记者怎么知道人家在这里见面………</p>\n<p>@朝****腹：嗯，一线医生特别辛苦，这点毋庸置疑，只是我不喜欢这种宣传手段。</p>\n<p>@什****018：这属于摆拍了吧，虽然我们对于医务工作者很尊敬，但是这属于明显的摆拍了，以后这种摆拍的新闻还是不要发了。</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"ZLxpvEmhZn\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/07/%e9%82%b1%e5%85%b5-%e5%a4%a7%e6%b2%b3%e5%a5%94%e6%b5%81-%e6%88%91%e5%bf%83%e6%be%8e%e6%b9%83%e5%a6%82%e6%98%a8/\">邱兵 | 大河奔流 我心澎湃如昨</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《邱兵 | 大河奔流 我心澎湃如昨》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/07/%e9%82%b1%e5%85%b5-%e5%a4%a7%e6%b2%b3%e5%a5%94%e6%b5%81-%e6%88%91%e5%bf%83%e6%be%8e%e6%b9%83%e5%a6%82%e6%98%a8/embed/#?secret=ZLxpvEmhZn\" data-secret=\"ZLxpvEmhZn\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><a class=\"st_tag internal_tag\" title=\"Posts tagged with CDS档案\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/cds%e6%a1%a3%e6%a1%88/\" rel=\"tag\">CDS档案</a>|<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E6%AD%A6%E6%B1%89%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E\">武汉肺炎</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-632597 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,38912,39707],"tags":[9540,39775,39646,13381,39648]}